  "text": "-Persuasiveness prediction is a useful tool to assess whether a model can measure how well a sentence can achieve its intended goal. This aspect is orthogonal to the determination of the goal itself, and is arguably equally important. [CITATION_1] . STILT is a further pretraining step on a datarich task before the final fine-tuning evaluation on the target task. We finetune BERT on three of such tasks:",
